# RPC via Protocol Buffers

## Source of truth
- Define APIs in `proto/**.proto` only; no REST endpoints.
- Example: `proto/echo/v1/echo.proto` with `EchoService`.

## Generation
- Requires `protoc` and dev dependency `ts-proto`.
- Generate TS to `src/proto/`:

```bash
pnpm proto:gen
```

## Tips
- Version your packages and services (`echo.v1`).
- Keep messages backwards compatible when possible.

